<%= content_for :page_title, 'About Us - GraceLife Medical Systems' %>
<h2 class="text-center text-primary">About Us</h2>
<hr>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-offset-2 col-md-8">
    <div class="jumbotron">
      <p class="spacing">
        <b class="main-text-orange">Gracelife Medical Systems Inc.</b> is an emerging global leader in EMR & EHR systems solutions in North America
        The healthcare industry is experiencing technological revolution. It is only a matter of time before the
        physicians and Hospital management will be over whelmed and will be at a cross road. The frequently asked
        questions (FAQs) will be "What are we focusing on? Our patients, or the 'How', which is the support system?"
        There will be challenges arising from Privacy of Personal Health Records (PHI) to Security of digital
        information on one hand. And the constant fast changing supporting technologies that tend to drain the
        purse of Hospitals.
      </p>
      <hr>
      <p class="spacing">
        <b class="main-text-orange">Gracelife Medical Systems (GMS)</b> is here to take that burden off your shoulders.
        We carry this out by providing Hosting Services, the best Cloud Solutions, Privacy Impact Assessment (PIA) on your data, and the best cost effective Security Solutions. We manage your projects from site inspection, to 24/7 help desk support services.
        Our vision is to help the Healthcare world succeed and in a profitable way. Let's get you the help you need.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="team">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">
        <div class="col-lg-12">
          <h3 class="text-center text-primary">OUR TEAM</h3>
          <hr>
          <div class="row pt-md">
            <% @users.each do |user| %>
                <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-3 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 profile">
                  <div class="img-box">
                    <% if user.image? %>
                        <%= image_tag user.image, size: '200x100', class: 'img-responsive' %>
                    <% end %>
                    <ul class="text-center">
                      <% if user.facebook? %>
                          <li><a href=<%= "https://#{user.facebook}" %>><i class="fa fa-facebook"></i></a></li>
                      <% end %>
                      <% if user.twitter? %>
                          <li><a href=<%= "https://#{user.twitter}" %>><i class="fa fa-twitter"></i></a></li>
                      <% end %>
                      <% if user.linkedin %>
                          <li><a href=<%= "https://#{user.linkedin}" %>><i class="fa fa-linkedin"></i></a></li>
                      <% end %>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                  <h1><%= link_to user.name, user_path(user) %></h1>
                  <h2><%= user.work_title %></h2>
                  <p><%= truncate(user.description, length: 60) %></p>
                </div>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>